&#xD;
          -  Anemia without iron deficiency&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Iron overload&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Jehovah's witnesses&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Endocarditis&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Treating neoplasia&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Uncontrolled hypertension&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  With infection&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Alfa-epoetin hypersensitivity&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Hypersensitivity of hamster's protein&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Erythroblastopenia induced by erythropoietin&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Ferinject or mannitol allergy&#xD;
      </textblock>
